column2: "Did you make a new route because we'll have different results due to us being used to the same route?"
"Be that as it may, there are many people that would readily hesitate without a guide."
"That's why you're a diamond among coals. I am your nominator. Yes, yes! There's no mistaking that I'll be fine with you."
"So, do you think you couldn't wrap this up for me lickety-split? Could you manage Very Hard?"
